" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Pemphigus foliaceus",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 428px; height: 300px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Pemphigus foliaceus is characterized by erythema, scaling, and crusting that first appears on the face and scalp, and later involves the chest and back.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
